      "cooked": "<p>pse ‘tokesor’ ishte me shume si pyetje sesa analog vs. digital (qe ka nje dekade qekur nisem ta aplikojme) <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=5\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>\n<p>ps. je qe je, mund te te pyes: a i shef rubrikat anesore te faqes ppu ne desktop view, me faqen e re?<br>\nUne jo.</p>",
